WEBVTT


00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:03.300
I think I will ask god why for the rest of my life.

00:00:04.360 --> 00:00:06.500
And never will I come to understand him.

00:00:08.480 --> 00:00:11.700
Even if god himself came in front of me and told me the reason,

00:00:11.720 --> 00:00:13.620
I don't think I would accept him.

00:00:16.400 --> 00:00:19.460
Some loves are too hard to bear.

00:00:20.440 --> 00:00:22.500
And with great love comes great pain.

00:00:23.680 --> 00:00:25.100
And with great loss

00:00:26.520 --> 00:00:27.980
comes the greatest pain.

00:00:30.280 --> 00:00:32.140
If love could have saved you,

00:00:33.520 --> 00:00:34.940
you would have lived forever.
